Uses Chrome's V8 Engine for fast execution.

2. Asynchronous and Non-Blocking

Can handle multiple requests simultaneously.

3. Single Language

JavaScript can be used for both frontend and backend.

4. Scalable

Can support a large number of users.

5. Large Package Ecosystem

